                <h2>About Bechdel Test</h2>
                <p>The Bechdel Test is a simple way to gauge the nature of women's presence in movies (and other works of fiction). For a movie to pass this test, the criteria is as follows:<br>

1. The movie must have atleast two women (with names) <br>
2. Who talk to each other <br>
3. About anything but a man.</p>
                <p>The test has been run on English movies for many years now and there is ample data (even APIs) and research material available. However, there is no such data available for Tamil Cinema. This project will serve as a platform for a crowd sourcing the data and results of the Bechdel test for Tamil movie. We hope to make the platform language agnostic in the future.</p>
               
